snippet.title: Inazuma Eleven 3 - Trailer (Nintendo 3DS)
snippet.description:
Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt and Inazuma Eleven 3: Bomb Blast are released on the 27th of September 2013 exclusively for the Nintendo 3DS family of handhelds.

Official sites:
Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt - http://www.nintendo.co.uk/Games/Nintendo-3DS/Inazuma-Eleven-3-Lightning-Bolt-796260.html
Inazuma Eleven 3: Bomb Blast - http://www.nintendo.co.uk/Games/Nintendo-3DS/Inazuma-Eleven-3-Bomb-Blast-796144.html
